<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" ?><?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" href="..\config8\suzuki.xsl" ?><!DOCTYPE suzuki [<!ENTITY % sdatacharaents SYSTEM "..\config8\sdatacharaents.txt">%sdatacharaents;]><suzuki><manual>
<section sectnbr = "1H">
<servcat sctnbr = "01" scnbr = "08">
<configtype typenbr = "0">
<servinfotype sitcode = "6">
<servinfo servinfosgmlid = "AENAP70A1806005" svcinfotypenbr = "08" svcinfoqualnbr = "03" page = "2" supplyoff = "1" modify = "0">
<title>
Ignition Timing Inspection
</title>
<attention3>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Ignition timing is not adjustable. If ignition timing is not as specified, check components related to ignition system.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
For identification of each cylinder, refer to 
<intxref refid = "AENAP70A1101001">Statement on Cleanliness and Care</intxref>
.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</attention3>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Connect scan tool to DLC (1) with ignition “OFF”.
</ptxt>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L1H001">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "NNNNN-00024">
SUZUKI scan tool (SUZUKI-SDT)
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A180005.jpg" width = "88.000mm" height = "67.502mm" ver = "01" gw = "159" gh = "175"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Start engine and warm it up to normal operating temperature.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Make sure that all electrical loads except ignition system are switched off.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Check that idle speed is within specification referring to 
<intxref refid = "AENAP70A1106001">Idle Speed and IAC Throttle Valve Opening Inspection</intxref>
.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Check ignition timing as following step.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
If either of check result is out of specification, check the following points.
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
CKP sensor
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
CKP sensor plate
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
ECM and its circuit
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
CMP sensor
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
CMP sensor rotor tooth of camshaft
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Crankshaft
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Crankshaft pulley
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Crankshaft pulley key
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
<s2>
<ptxt>
Check that ignition timing is within specification using SUZUKI scan tool.
</ptxt>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>
Set timing light (1) to ignition coil harness for No.1 cylinder and check that ignition timing is within specification.
</ptxt>
</s2>
<spec-sdm>
<sdm-title>
Ignition timing
</sdm-title>
<sdm1>
<sdm-condition>
</sdm-condition>
<sdm-value>
1&#176; to 15&#176; BTDC (at specified idle speed)
</sdm-value>
</sdm1>
</spec-sdm>
<spec>
<title>
Ignition order
</title>
<ptxt>
1 – 3 – 4 – 2
</ptxt>
</spec>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L1H002">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09930-76420">
09930–76420
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
<servicetoolitem id = "L1H003">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09930-76310">
09930–76310
</s-number>
<ptxt>
</ptxt>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I7V20A180007.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "52.060mm" ver = "01" gw = "178" gh = "131"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
With engine idling, check that increasing engine speed advances ignition timing.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
If the check result is not satisfactory, check the following points.
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
ECM and its circuit: 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENAP70A1104070"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
TP sensor: 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENAP70A1306004"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
APP sensor: 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENAP70A1306006"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</s1>
</servinfo>
</servinfotype>
</configtype>
</servcat>
</section></manual></suzuki>
